title: Family Guy S01E01 - Death Has A Shadow
description: In this first episode of the series, Peter goes out to a friend&#039;s bachelor party, but first promises Lois that he won&#039;t get drunk. He does, of course, and the resulting hangover causes him to lose his job the next day. After several unsuccessful attempts to get a new job, Peter applies for welfare, only to discover that a clerical error has now made the family rich. Things spin further out of Peter&#039;s control, while Lois is still unaware that her husband has been fired.
